│  │ DELETE /users/1         → Delete user                   │   │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
│                                                                 │
│  ORDERS RESOURCE:                                               │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │ GET /orders             → Get all orders                │   │
│  │ GET /orders/5           → Get specific order            │   │
│  │ POST /orders            → Create order                  │   │
│  │ GET /users/1/orders     → Get orders of user 1          │   │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
│                                                                 │
│  REST PRINCIPLES:                                               │
│  ✓ Use HTTP methods properly                                    │
│  ✓ Resources have unique URLs                                   │
│  ✓ Stateless (no session stored on server)                      │
│  ✓ Standard format for requests/responses                       │
│                                                                 │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

