### Authentication & Authorization Flow

```
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│        AUTHENTICATION vs AUTHORIZATION                 │
├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                        │
│  AUTHENTICATION (Who are you?)                         │
│  ───────────────────────────────                      │
│   Client sends credentials                            │
│        ↓                                               │
│   Server verifies identity                            │
│        ↓                                               │
│   Server returns TOKEN/SESSION                        │
│        ↓                                               │
│   Result: ✓ You are John Doe                          │
│                                                        │
│  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────    │
│                                                        │
│  AUTHORIZATION (What can you do?)                      │
│  ──────────────────────────────────                   │
│   Client sends request with token                     │
│        ↓                                               │
│   Server reads token                                  │
│        ↓                                               │
│   Server checks permissions/roles                     │
│        ↓                                               │
│   Result: ✓ You can view reports OR                  │
│           ✗ You can't delete users                    │
│                                                        │
│  EXAMPLE:                                              │
│  ────────                                             │
│  1. Login with username/password                      │
│     → Authentication (verified you're John)           │
│                                                        │
│  2. Try to access "Admin Dashboard"                   │
│     → Authorization check                             │
│     → Your role = "user", not "admin"                 │
│     → Denied! (403 Forbidden)                         │
│                                                        │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

